    Description
    Administrator
    Represents an Administrator, a user with administrative privileges.
    Doctor
    Represents a Doctor, a type of User with the ability to manage appointments, set availability, prescribe medicine, and handle appointment outcomes.
    Patient
    Represents a Patient, a type of User who has medical records and can schedule, reschedule, and cancel appointments, as well as manage appointment outcomes.
    Pharmacist
    Represents a Pharmacist, a type of User with a specific age.
    Receptionist
    Represents a Receptionist, a type of User with a specific age.
    User
    Represents a User in the system with an ID, name, gender, and password.
